## Clockgenerator mit Commandblocks
## Code example for my Youtube tutorial videos
## Video: https://youtu.be/ZgoUJcxnHVQ

## Init
scoreboard objectives remove Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock
scoreboard objectives add Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock dummy
scoreboard players set _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock 0

## Die Clock
scoreboard players add _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock 1
execute if score _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock matches 40.. run scoreboard players set _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock 0

## Auswertung
# >= 0 und <= 30
execute if score _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock matches 0.. if score _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock matches ..30

# = 2
execute if score _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock matches 2
tellraw @a "Hier"

# = 4
execute if score _takt Tutorial_Scoreboard_Clock matches 4
tellraw @a "Hier2"

